<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>matirai koṇṭa kōppara kēcari paṉmaṟkku yāṇṭu <num value="30">3 <g type="numeral">10</g></num> Āvatu teṉkarai <hi rend="grantha">bra</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">hma</hi>tEyam <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kaṇṭa <hi rend="grantha">ca</hi>tu<hi rend="grantha">rvvedi</hi> maṅkalattu teṉkayilāyattu <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>varkku Eṟumpiyūruṭai
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yāṉ nakkanākaṉ Oru nontāviḷakku <hi rend="grantha">candrādi</hi>ttavan Eriya koṇṭu tanta nilamiyūr vaṭapiṭākaiyi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>l nilam <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yāriṭai nāṉ vilai koṇṭu Iṟaiyiḻiccik kuṭutta nilamāvatu karampaiyil
<lb n="5"/>nilamēlpāṟkkellai murukkūr vāykkālukku kiḻakku vaṭapāṟkellai kaṇakkappēṟ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟukkut teṟkku kīḻpāṟkkellai <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kaṇṭa vāykkālukku mēṟkku kōl viḻunta vāṟṟāl van
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ta pattucceyyum <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yāriṭai vilaikoṇṭu Iṟaikkup poṉkuṭuttu Iṟaikāval kaṭavā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rāka vaittēṉ nakkaṉākaṉēṉ Itu <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara rakṣai <g type="ddanda">.</g><g type="dashLong">.</g></hi>
</p>

